---
title: BBQ Chicken Bites & Loaded Fries with Chunky Salsa, Extra Cheddar Cheese & Garlic Sauce
description: We think we’ve done the impossible - taken a glorious plate of golden fries and made them even better. Pile them high with sweet and savoury barbecue chicken, a fresh tomato salsa, and lots and lots of Cheddar cheese. Who could possibly resist?
